description:
A man who had lost everything.

An almighty power, the [Zero Code] held within his hand.

&ldquo;Player Kim Su Hyun, do you truly wish to revert the time of Hall Plain?&rdquo;

&ldquo;I want to go back 10 years. To that period when I first came here.&rdquo;

Based in the same universe as &quot;Second Coming of Gluttony&quot;.
